public class WrappedEnvironment
extends org.oslo.ocl20.semantics.bridge.impl.EnvironmentImpl

Allows to set an instance of this class as parent of a given environment. The class is used by the QVTRParser class to enable AST creation of QVT-R scripts.

Version:
0.1
Author:
Kapova et al., Sebastian Lehrig (lehrig@mail.upb.de)
